Activity, LinkListener
public class Empty
extends AbstractBasicActivity

There is often a need to use an activity that does nothing, for example when a fault needs to be caught and suppressed. The empty activity is used for this purpose. Another use of empty is to provide a synchronization point in a flow. [10.8]
